    <div class="AssessmentProblem.identifier">102642</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.type">RestrictedConstructedResponse</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.statement"><p>Mai's mom makes 1 serving of tea by mixing 2 teaspoons of honey into 1 cup of tea.</p>

<ol>
	<li>How much honey and tea does she need to make 4 servings of her tea recipe?</li>
	<li>Explain one way she could make tea that is sweeter than her usual tea.</li>
	<li>Explain one way she could make tea that is less sweet than her usual tea.</li>
</ol>
</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.solution"><ol>
	<li>4 cups of tea and 8 teaspoons of honey.
	<p><img class="h-max-height--6-lines" src="/image_files/30672.png" /></p>
	</li>
	<li>Answers vary. Sample response: she can add 3 teaspoons of honey to 1&#xA0;cup of tea.</li>
	<li>Answers vary. Sample response: she can add 1 teaspoon of honey to 1&#xA0;cup of tea.</li>
</ol>
</div>
